Package gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc

Class TimeInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc.TimeInterval
  • public class TimeInterval
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a time interval. That is, a continuous interval of time from a beginning time to an end time. The beginning and ending time values may have a null value to represent time infinitely in the past or future respectively.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    B. Harris
